      "type": "accordion_inline",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_item_jKtQnJ": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How can I get free shipping?",
            "content": "We are pleased to offer free delivery for orders over $100 shipped to most locations within Canada and the United States. However, please note that there are a few postal codes which may not be eligible for free shipping. In cases of oversized packages, a flat rate fee of $9.99 will be applied. You will be automatically eligible for free shipping once your subtotal reaches $100 and this option will be shown at checkout. Kindly note that all orders eligible for free shipping will be shipped via ground service.<br><br>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_nWPkrx": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I pick up my order in-store?",
            "content": "Absolutely! We offer free in-store pickup at checkout, and you will receive instructions via email. Orders are typically available within a few hours during store business hours.  <br><br>\n\n\nMonday to Wednesday |\t10am - 6pm<br>\nThursday to Friday |\t10am - 8pm<br>\nSaturday\t  9am - 6pm\nSunday\t10am - 5pm"
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_c4CmUc": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long will shipping take?",
            "content": "Our goal is to ensure that all orders are shipped out the same day or the following day, wherever possible. The estimated transit times for ground shipping are as follows:<br><br>\n\nWestern Canada: 1-4 business days<br>\nEastern Canada: 4-6 business days<br>\nUSA: 3-8 business days<br>\nInternational: 5-10 business days<br><br>\nPlease note that these are just estimates and not guarantees. The actual transit times may vary depending on the package dimensions and the final destination. If you have selected express shipping, the transit time will be shown at checkout and typically takes 1-3 days to deliver.<br><br>\n\nHowever, please note that sticks require additional handling and may arrive a day later than another package if the order is a multi-piece shipment.<br><br>\n\nFor additional questions about our shipping policy, please contact us at <b><a href=\"mailto:sales@thehockeyshop.com\">sales@thehockeyshop.com<\/a><\/b> or call us via <b><a href=\"tel:1-800-567-7790\">1-800-567-7790.<\/a><\/b>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_tcEFQY": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I order from outside of Canada?",
            "content": "Certainly! We offer a variety of products that can be shipped to the US and other countries. To view our international selection, please click on <b>International Store.<\/b> However, some of our products are only available for shipping to Canadian addresses. To identify these items, please look for the <b><i>\"Ships Canada Only\"<\/i><\/b> icon on the product page. This icon indicates that the manufacturer has imposed shipping limitations on the product.<br><br>\n\nFor instance, Bauer products cannot be shipped outside of Canada, and CCM, True, and Warrior products also have their own shipping restrictions in place."
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_pRgLPn": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How can I ensure my that my package is protected?",
            "content": "Safeguard your package for just $1.99 with premium shipping protection during checkout. <br><br>\nWe will quickly replace and resend your order if it gets lost or damaged. <br><br>\n\nIf your order is marked as delivered but there's no sign of the package, wait at least 1 business day before hitting the panic button. Unfortunately, it is common for couriers to mark an item as delivered well before the delivery attempt is made. After waiting a day, reach out to our team at sales@thehockeyshop.com to resolve the issue. <br><br>\n\nPackages that are unprotected will follow the standard claims policy of the shipping courier which can take additional time and the final decision is up to the discretion of the courier."
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_VnUDx7": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do you ship hockey sticks?",
            "content": "Great question! We have custom boxes designed for that! The box works as a large envelope or sleeve and will secure the stick and protect it in transit. We can ship up to 4 sticks per box."
          }
        }
