        "accordion_item_3cPfTU": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I process a warranty claim?",
            "content": "If you're here because an item is faulty or defective...sorry to hear! We'll work to get that item replaced for you. Our store carries many brands that offer extensive warranties for premature breakage, which means you could receive a replacement product. If you're located in Surrey, BC, our retail location is ready to assist you. However, if you're shopping from out of town, you can submit a warranty claim digitally using photos of the item. You can find information for each brand on our website under Warranty Information. This page outlines all warranty timelines, policies, and procedures."
          }
        },
        "accordion_item_VyQCQz": {
          "type": "accordion_item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Which items have a warranty?",
            "content": "Nearly all the hockey and goalie products we sell are covered by a manufacturer's warranty. For a full list of products covered by warranty, visit our Warranty Information page. Pro stock equipment is not covered under warranty as these items have been built specifically for professional players."
